{"tid":2217902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚德塞指特朗普無任何好理由將美國從世衛退出","createTime":"2020-09-25T20:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T01:38:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff65e756e93131a61e40ce10d721483fd5d3f90","tid":2217902,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T20:04:45.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞說，美國總統特朗普沒有任何好的理由，將美國從世衛中退出。<br />\n<br />\n在新型肺炎疫情肆虐全球期間，特朗普多次批評世衛抗疫不力，以及未能要求中國對疫情大流行負責。他曾在今年5月揚言，終止美國與世衛之間的關係。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞最新接受訪問時表示，當知道特朗普說要將美國退出世衛時，他第一個反應是「不相信」，又說直至現在，他依然認為美國行政當局，找不到好的理由退出世衛。<br />\n<br />\n他說難以確定若美國退出世衛帶來的影響，強調相比美國對世衛的財政貢獻，他更加重視美國在全球的領導能力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551723-20200926.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551723-20200926.htm&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=fd42511c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551723-20200926.htm&h=fc75ab55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551723-20200926.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9766916c15c02caf1a1bd427614703ae068b7a38","tid":2217902,"uid":273703,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T20:06:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a4b8f8775327529568be1d7452dff6628bae7dd","tid":2217902,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T20:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9305dea5b30f976cd87bc420826a195562e80851","tid":2217902,"uid":263150,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T20:21:32.000Z","msg":"未計全球，淨係放流料死咗20萬美國人&hellip;<br />\n都夠晒理由啦"},{"pid":"f87119f42fbb09ee21f26684ab4bb6fa92ec97c0","tid":2217902,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T20:22:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d57778cfdebcd1f1a54e60919294326e0b1b